Name: Maze Dungeon
About the game: Maze Dungeon is an action roguelite game with 3D Voxel graphics . This game is inspired by collectible and growing roguelite games like Binding of Isaac and Risk of Rain . Navigate through a dungeon full of various equipment, unique artifacts , maze-like complex dungeons, and powerful enemies . Grow your character You can level up by killing monsters in the dungeon to gain experience points. Each character class has its own unique skills, and enhance your skills to defeat enemies with your own skillset . Acquire various equipment Players can acquire different grades of equipment in the dungeon, and various enchantments exist. Get powerful equipment to strengthen your character Collect unique and powerful artifacts Maze Dungeon has unique and powerful artifacts . Collect various artifacts and clear the dungeon . Procedurally generated complex dungeons In Maze Dungeon, dungeons are created in a procedurally complex and diverse manner for each stage rather than a fixed structure. As the stage progresses, more complex and powerful enemies appear. Various unlockable classes conditions to unlock various classes. Each character has unique stats and skills, and offers a variety of play styles.
